<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Accessible Eats</title>

<style>
body {
  margin: 0;
  font-family: Arial;
  background: #f8f8f8;
  color: #333;
}

header {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff6b6b, #ff8e53);
  color: white;
  text-align: center;
  padding: 2rem;
}

header h1 {
  margin: 0;
  font-size: 2.5rem;
}

nav {
  background: #222;
  padding: 1rem;
  text-align: center;
}

nav a {
  color: white;
  margin: 0 15px;
  text-decoration: none;
  font-weight: bold;
}

.container {
  max-width: 900px;
  margin: auto;
  padding: 20px;
}

.card {
  background: white;
  padding: 20px;
  margin-bottom: 15px;
  border-radius: 10px;
  box-shadow: 0 3px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
}

button {
  background: #ff6b6b;
  border: none;
  padding: 12px;
  color: white;
  border-radius: 6px;
  cursor: pointer;
}

.hero {
  text-align: center;
  padding: 40px 20px;
}

footer {
  background: #222;
  color: white;
  text-align: center;
  padding: 1rem;
}
</style>

</head>
<body>

<header>
<h1>Accessible Eats</h1>
<p>Affordable Meals. Real Impact.</p>
</header>

<nav>
<a href="#menu">Menu</a>
<a href="#ebook">eBook</a>
<a href="#contact">Contact</a>
</nav>

<div class="hero">
<h2>Eat Well Without Overspending</h2>
<p>Helping everyday people access affordable meals.</p>
</div>

<div class="container">

<h2 id="menu">Our Menu</h2>

<div class="card">Budget Burger - R25</div>
<div class="card">Chicken Wrap - R30</div>
<div class="card">Veggie Plate - R20</div>

<h2 id="ebook">Free eBook</h2>

<div class="card">
<p>Download our guide to eating well on a budget.</p>

<a href="Accessible_Eats_eBook.pdf" download>
<button>Download eBook</button>
</a>

</div>

<h2 id="contact">Contact</h2>

<div class="card">
<p>Phone: 071 234 5678</p>
<p>Location: Johannesburg</p>
</div>

</div>

<footer>
<p>© 2026 Accessible Eats</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
